results.name: Permutation of natural numbers: a(n) = A235489(A235201(n)).
comment: The permutation satisfies A000040(a(n)) = a(A000040(n)) for all positive n except for n=2.
In contrast to A235485/A235486 this permutation contains also infinite cycles.
